  Title: God in All Worlds
  Locus:
    Page: 154
  Source:
    Title: Blood Memory
By: Martha Graham
---
You will know the wonders of the human body because there is nothing more
wonderful. The next time you look into the mirror, just look at the way
the ears rest next to the head; look at the way the hairline grows; think
of all the little bones in your wrist. It is a miracle.
